Usage: getPtnPinStatus [-help] [-cell <partitionName>]
                       [-pin {pinName | pinNameList}]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-cell <partitionName>            # Specifies name of the partition, wildcard
                                 # can be specified (string, optional)
-pin {pinName | pinNameList}     # Specifies name of the partition pins,
                                 # wildcard can be specified (string, optional)